com.jed.actor

Class Boundary

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jed.actor.Boundary
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Displayable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CircleBoundary, PolygonBoundary, RectangleBoundary

    public abstract class Boundary
extends Object
implements Displayable
    Abstract class who associates another AbstractEntity as an "owner." The owner's boundary is defined by a subclass of Boundary's implementation.
    Since:
    0.1.0
    Author:
    jlinde, Peter Colapietro
    See Also:
